{
  "stem": "20616.4",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "We'll take it out of here first couple of weeks salary, whatever you earn.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "But you have to have a car.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And I always wanted a car and my parents never had a car.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And I said, this is my excuse to get a car.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "I had a little bit of money saved from before and my mother saved all the money that I sent back from the army, my-- she bought bonds from that and so on.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "Well, I didn't use that money.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "That became my dowry later on.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "But I had enough money to buy, I think was $100 for a-- $300 for a car that was an ancient jalopy, which lasted about three weeks and I just couldn't use it for work and I got rid of it, got myself a little better car.",
      "word_count": 47
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "But I found out-- I learned how to take baby pictures.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "And what happened was they said, oh you don't have to-- I didn't know what the front or back of a baby was.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "And they said, we'll train you.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "So they sent me out with a guy who had been working there for two weeks before.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "And he took me to one or two sittings.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "He said, well, you put up a table; you put the baby on there; you put one light here; you [? put ?] one light there; you put the background up; and you try to get the baby to smile.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "[SIGHS]",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we went to one or two sittings and he said, well, I've got to go.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I have an appointment someplace.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They'll send you out with somebody else in the morning.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I went back in the morning.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They said, well, we have so much work to do, you'll have to do the best you can.",
      "word_count": 18
    }
  ],
